premise_source_doc_sentence: John William Carson  (  October 23 , 1925 -- January 23 , 2005  )  was an American talk show host and comedian , best known for his 30 years as host of The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson  (  1962 -- 1992  )  .
The Johnny Carson Show is a 1955-56 half-hour prime time television variety show starring Johnny Carson .

Carson Entertainment Group  (  formerly Carson Productions and Carson Productions Group  )  is a television production company established by Johnny Carson in 1980 to primarily produce The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson from 1980 to 1992 and Late Night with David Letterman from 1982 to 1993 .

In a 1978 profile of Carson in The New Yorker , Kenneth Tynan described the Johnny Carson Show as `` a half-hour program that goes through seven directors , eight writers , and thirty-nine weeks of worsening health before expiring , in the spring of 1956 . ''
